Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This Padawan was a Jedi of the Jedi Order and trained under a Mikkian master. During the Clone Wars, the Padawan and their master were on the jungle planet of Ledeve to look into the world's Jedi Temple, although they were confronted by Grievous, a Separatist cyborg general. Grievous killed the master before slaying the Padawan and learning of the temple.
